  "texts": [
    "These URLs are then used as keys to look up their page content in a lookup table constructed from public crawl snapshots, which populates a set of pages for that query.",
    "In addition, the evaluation takes into account whether the URL is from the English Wikipedia.",
    "If so, the page title is extracted from the URL and the corresponding page is searched for in the Wikipedia dump.",
    "As researchers gain a better understanding of the strengths and weaknesses of various retrieval techniques, they are increasingly opting to combine them, as described above.",
    "This is done in the hope of further exploiting the advantages of these techniques to improve the effectiveness and robustness of the RALM architecture."
